    "title": {
      "rendered": "6 Clever Mobile Apps Created by Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17203\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Mobile Apps Nonprofit Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Mobile-Apps-Nonprofit-Facebook.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>All launched in 2014, the mobile apps listed below created by nonprofits clearly demonstrate that nonprofits are evolving in their approach to mobile apps. The hard truth is that <a href=\"http://info.localytics.com/blog/app-retention-improves\">only 39% of mobile apps are opened\u00a011 times or more</a>\u00a0and 20%\u00a0of apps are only opened once. That said,\u00a0the rapid\u00a0sales of smartphones worldwide ensure a growing a mobile app audience in coming years, but for nonprofit mobile apps to be successful they must be well-designed and useful. If your nonprofit is considering launching an app in 2015, be sure to do your research first.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. United Nations\u00a0Calendar of Observances</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The UN Calendar of Observances app provides details of UN observances as well as ways to get involved in related events.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/calendar-observances-making/id579193062\">iTunes</a> | <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.un.mobile.calendar&amp;hl=en\">Google Play</a>\u00a0| <a href=\"https://unp.un.org/calendar/\">United Nations</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://unp.un.org/calendar/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17188\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/UN-APP-Google-Play.png?resize=600%2C268\" alt=\"UN APP Google Play\" width=\"600\" height=\"268\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/UN-APP-Google-Play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/UN-APP-Google-Play.png?resize=300%2C134&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2.\u00a0SafeNight</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">When someone is in urgent need of safe shelter to escape domestic violence, SafeNight\u00a0enables users to make an immediate donation to pay for a hotel room for the person in need.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/US/app/id835672659\">iTunes</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.caravan.safenight&amp;hl=en\">Google Play</a>\u00a0| <a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/safenight/9bfaadea-2476-461a-b751-f80a8211849c\">Windows Phone</a> |\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.caravanstudios.org/#!safenight/cfvg\">Caravan Studios</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.caravanstudios.org/#!safenight/cfvg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17191\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/safe-night-google-play.png?resize=600%2C272\" alt=\"safe night google play\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/safe-night-google-play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/safe-night-google-play.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3.\u00a0iCitzen</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">iCitizen is an app that enables users to keep track of political issues and voice their opinions and thoughts directly to elected officials.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/icitizen-for-iphone/id725655449\">iTunes</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.icitizen\">Google Play</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://blog.icitizen.com/icitizen-and-headcount-announce-partnership-to-enhance-civic-engagement-and-citizen-involvement-in-government\">HeadCount</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.icitizen.com/icitizen-and-headcount-announce-partnership-to-enhance-civic-engagement-and-citizen-involvement-in-government\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17201\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/icitizen-app-google-play.png?resize=600%2C268\" alt=\"icitizen app google play\" width=\"600\" height=\"268\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/icitizen-app-google-play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/icitizen-app-google-play.png?resize=300%2C134&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4.\u00a0Food Scores</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Environmental Working Group\u2019s Food Scores app is a\u00a0consumers guide to healthy, affordable food that\u2019s good for people and the planet.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/ewg-food-scores/id930172079\">iTunes</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ewg.foodscores&amp;hl=en\">Google Play</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.ewg.org/foodscores\">Environmental Working Group</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.ewg.org/foodscores\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17198\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Food-Score-google-play.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Food Score google play\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Food-Score-google-play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Food-Score-google-play.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5.\u00a0Charity Navigator</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This app helps guide intelligent giving by providing ratings for nearly 7,000 charities based on their financial health, accountability and transparency.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/charity-navigator/id740191196\">iTunes</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.charitynavigator.mobile&amp;hl=en\">Google Play</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/charity-navigator/id740191196\">Charity Navigator</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/charity-navigator/id740191196\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17199\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Charity-Naviagor-Google-Play.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Charity Naviagor Google Play\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Charity-Naviagor-Google-Play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Charity-Naviagor-Google-Play.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Blood Donor</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This app enables users to find nearby Red Cross blood drives, schedule appointments, and earn rewards from premier retailers.<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/blood-donor-by-american-red/id911428916\">iTunes</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cube.arc.blood\">Google Play</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/safenight/9bfaadea-2476-461a-b751-f80a8211849c\">Windows Phone</a>\u00a0|\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.redcross.org/mobile-apps/blood-app\">Red Cross</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.redcross.org/mobile-apps/blood-app\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17193\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/red-cross-app-google-play.png?resize=600%2C278\" alt=\"red cross app google play\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/red-cross-app-google-play.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/red-cross-app-google-play.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
